snippet.title: Amber Heard And Elon Musk Take Their Relationship Public
snippet.description:
In late 2016, billionaire Elon Musk and actress Amber Heard were romantically linked for the first time. The relationship first hit the gossip pages just a few months after Musk filed for divorce from ex-wife Talulah Riley, whom he was married to and divorced from twice. Now, the two have taken their romance public. The actress and the tech Amber and Elon came out publicly as a couple in Australia, where Amber is filming 'Aquaman.' The two walked around Queensland, Australia, on Sunday with their arms around each other. The pair were spotted by the paparazzi. Later, the couple posted pictures from an intimate dinner on Musk's instagram page.

snippet.title: Amber Heard And Elon Musk Were Caught Kissing Despite Confirming Split
snippet.description:
Amber Heard And Elon Musk Were Caught Kissing Despite Confirming Split
Amber and Elon packed on the PDA during their recent lunch date, thus sparking rumors that the exes are getting back together.


After going through a controversial divorce from Johnny Depp, Amber Heard jumped into another high-profile relationship. She started going out with billionaire businessman Elon Musk after her split from the 54-year-old actor, but their romance ended after a year of dating. However, it seems that the exes are trying to rekindle their relationship as they were recently caught kissing after having lunch together.

Us Weekly shared PDA photos of Amber and Elon during their date in Los Angeles. The CEO of Tesla was spotted giving the 31-year-old actress a kiss on her lips, and she seemed to enjoy that special moment as well. They were also seen embracing each other before getting into their cars.

While Amber Heard and Elon Musk appear to be getting back together, a source close to the business magnate revealed that they are still in the friend zone. The Justice League actress reportedly invited her ex-boyfriend to her favorite restaurant for lunch. The PDA photo was just allegedly a friendly kiss to bid each other farewell and does not mean that they have reunited.

Since Elon was the one who initiated the kiss, this could probably mean that he still wants Amber back. During an interview with Rolling Stone, the 46-year-old investor confessed that he was really in love with the Austin-born actress and their split hurts him bad. He even explained that she broke up with him more than he broke up with her.

Musk also admitted that he is scared of being lonely, so that‚Äôs why he is looking for a serious companion and not just a one-night stand. The South African-born inventor has been married twice ‚Äì first with Canadian author Justine Musk and second with English actress Talulah Riley. Heard, on the other hand, has only been married once and that was to Johnny Depp.

Elon Musk confessed that he cannot be happy if he is not in love, so he may still have feelings for Amber Heard. The founder of SpaceX has a big chance of winning back the blonde beauty because they are on good terms despite their split. The Danish Girl star explained on Instagram that she prefers to remain quiet when it comes to their relationship. She even assured her followers that even after breaking up, they still care deeply for one another and remain close.

It may probably take time before Elon Musk and Amber Heard reunite for good, but their recent kissing and dates may help bring the exes closer.

snippet.title: Elon Musk Denies Having a Threesome with Amber Heard and Cara Delevingne - Abcs News
snippet.description:
Elon Musk is speaking out against one of the more salacious claims to come up in the messy and extremely contentious fallout from Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's marriage.
According to a deposition from Depp's ongoing defamation lawsuit against his ex-wife, the ex of Amber's friend Raquel Pennington claimed Raquel told him Heard, Musk and model Cara Delevingne had a "threeway affair." While he wasn't sure when it happened, Depp's lawyer specifically asked whether it was in November 2016, which would have been months after her split from Depp -- but before they were legally divorced.
While neither Heard or Delevingne have addressed the gossip, Musk denied it to Page Six.
"Cara and I are friends, but we've never been intimate," he said. "She would confirm this."
"Also, I wish to confirm again that Amber and I only started going out about a month after her divorce filing," he continued. "I don't think I was ever even in the vicinity of Amber during their marriage!

snippet.title: Amber Heard and Elon Musk: Spotted Together in Chile after being seen sharing a kiss.
snippet.description:
Amber Heard and Elon Musk: Spotted Together in Chile after being seen sharing a kiss.

The former couple was seen on vacation in Chile and enjoying a dinner with friends that included the brother of Tesla CEO Kimbal Musk. The restaurant where they were having dinner, El Taringa, published a photo of the crew with the actress and the engineer sitting next to each other in the left corner of the photo on Friday night. Heard, 31, was staring at the table while Musk, 46, was enjoying a conversation with his fellow diners. What an inspiration to have had Kimbal Musk and his family in Taringa. Thank you for sharing your ideas about sustainable supply chains The Kitchen and its whole concept is a model to follow. While the actress of the Justice League has not published photos of her with Musk, she did share photos of her vacation on Saturday while having fun on the beach with a dress, a hat and a necklace of roses.

Heard and Musk made headlines a few days before Christmas when they were photographed sharing a kiss outside a Los Angeles restaurant. The photos left the fans speculating whether the two had rekindled their romance four months after the separation. A source close to Musk said the duo was just having a friendly visit. Amber invited Elon to his favorite breakfast place in Texas, said Musk's friend from HomeState Restaurant, Los Feliz, California. where the photos were taken. They shared a quick goodbye kiss. They are still just friends, without trying to be together again.

snippet.title: Amber Heard and Elon Musk Walk Arm-in-Arm During First Public Outing Together
snippet.description:
Amber Heard and Elon Musk are spending some time in the land down under! 

The actress is currently filming Aquaman in Australia, and on Sunday she took a well-deserved break for an afternoon adventure with the billionaire Tesla founder. Amber and Elon were photographed with their arms around each other, strolling through Currumbin Wildlife Sanctuary as they prepared to embark on the attraction's zip lining course. 

Amber, 31, was all smiles in a simple T-shirt, jeans and light pink highlights throughout her typically-blond tresses. Two of the mogul's six sons reportedly joined Heard and Musk for the day trip.

This marks the pair's first public outing together since romance rumors began to swirl nearly nine months ago.

snippet.title: Elon Musk Denies Threesome With Ex Amber Heard and Cara Delevingne | THE DAILY NEWS
snippet.description:
Elon Musk Denies Having a Threesome With Ex Amber Heard and Cara Delevingne


Not the case! Elon Musk spoke out after being accused of having a ‚Äúthree-way affair‚Äù with his ex Amber Heard and Cara Delevingne.
Celebrity Sex Confessions

‚ÄúCara and I are friends, but we‚Äôve never been intimate. She would confirm this,‚Äù the Tesla CEO, 48, said in a statement to Page Six on Thursday, June 18. ‚ÄúAlso, I wish to confirm again that Amber and I only started going out about a month after her divorce filing. I don‚Äôt think I was ever even in the vicinity of Amber during their marriage!‚Äù


Musk‚Äôs response came one day after the Daily Mail reported that Josh Drew, a friend and former neighbor of Heard and her ex-husband Johnny Depp, participated in a deposition in the former couple‚Äôs ongoing legal battle. Drew, who was previously married to the actress‚Äô MMA fighter pal Raquel ‚ÄúRocky‚Äù Pennington, reportedly claimed that Musk, Heard, 34, and Delevingne, 27, had a threesome at the Pirates of the Caribbean star‚Äôs Los Angeles home in late 2016.

‚ÄúThey were having a three-way affair, correct?‚Äù attorney Benjamin Chew asked during the deposition, according to the U.K. newspaper, to which Drew responded, ‚ÄúMy understanding, yes.‚Äù


Musk was previously accused of having an affair with Heard before she filed for divorce from Depp, 57, in May 2016 after one year of marriage. The SpaceX founder denied the allegation at the time.

On Thursday, Musk urged the Rum Diary costars to ‚Äúbury the hatchet and move on‚Äù as their messy legal drama continues to make headlines more than three years after they finalized their divorce.

‚ÄúLife is too short for such extended negativity,‚Äù the tech entrepreneur told Page Six. ‚ÄúNobody is going to say, after it‚Äôs all over, that they wished the court battle had lasted longer!‚Äù


Musk and Heard were in an on-off relationship from 2016 to 2018. He is now dating Grimes, with whom he welcomed a son named X AE A-XII in May, the same month Delevingne split from Ashley Benson.

snippet.title: Stars Who Can't Stand Elon Musk
snippet.description:
Is he a real-life Tony Stark, or a real-life supervillain? A space pioneer, or just a mega-rich guy who can't stop tweeting? Billionaire Elon Musk is a divisive figure, to say the least. From union-busting to busted Teslas, Musk has made a lot of people upset, many of whom are among the most famous folks in Hollywood.

What did Musk do to tick off George Clooney, of all people? Is rapper Azealia Banks telling the truth about her wild weekend with Musk and Grimes? And why did Jeopardy! champ Ken Jennings join the fray? Here are some stars who simply can't stand Elon Musk.

#ElonMusk #Stars #Actors

George Clooney had enough of his Tesla | 0:00
Mark Zuckerberg isn't a friend | 1:07
Sarah Palin called Tesla 'a loser' | 2:21
Grimes' mom is over Elon | 3:13
Jeff Bezos went from friend to foe | 4:24
Azealia Banks' wild ride | 5:48

snippet.title: Amber Heard & Elon Musk Go Ziplining Down Under with His Kids
snippet.description:
Amber Heard & Elon Musk Go Ziplining Down Under with His Kids
AMBER HEARD
ELON MUSK GO OUT ON A LINE FOR ME

Elon Musk and Amber Heard strapped up and held on tight ... for a little semi-extreme fun in Australia.
The couple went ziplining in the Currumbin Wildlife Sanctuary on the Gold Coast. The actress and Tesla honcho had a lot on the line here, and not just because he was trusting his multi-billion dollar ass to a safety harness.
Two of Elon's 6 sons came along, so Amber had the added pressure of being dad's cool gf. She probably scored some bonus points, since she's Down Under to shoot "Aquaman" with Jason Momoa.
Looks like the couple -- coming up on 1 year together -- had a good time. Still, we gotta say ... no one, not even Elon with his riches, looks good in those helmets.
It's just a thing.

snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs. Elon Musk
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp vs. Elon Musk
______________________________________________
For more videos subscribe : https://bit.ly/2zoPgqj
______________________________________________
Johnny Depp has filed a $50 million lawsuit against ex wife Amber Heard , as time goes more and more high-profile stars have been caught in the middle.And now Tesla CEO Elon Musk has been wrapped up in the drama as well. 
In today's video we are going to discuss about Johnny Depp reportedly dragging Elon Musk into the libel case against Amber Heard. 

Last week Johnny Depp's side things received good news when it was announced that his defamation case against Amber Heard would be going forward in Virginia following reports that covid19 concerns would place the trial on hold days prior. Depp's allegations come after Amber Heard's 2018 Washington Post op-ed, where she accused the Fantastic Beasts actor of domestic violence. Depp denies these claims and has called them an "elaborate hoax" to advance her own career. 

British newspaper Metro.co.uk was first to report that Depp's attorney has issued a subpoena against Musk ,the Tesla CEO and Heard's former boyfriend.New York Post website page six also followed up with a similar story hours later. 

The latest development in the legal battle involves an alleged affair Johnny Depp claims Amber Heard had with tech mogul Elon Musk while they were still married. Heard and Musk have confirmed to have been in a relationship shortly after The Rum Diary co-stars called it quits in 2016, but Depp has gathered information that points to the two possibly being together before that. 

Depp's attorney Adam Waldman told the publications ,"We have now issued subpoenas to Amber Heard, her hoax assisting friends, Elon Musk and other witnesses to explain the avalanche of the video, Audio, photographic and testimonial evidence with which we intend to confront them." 

A source told page six, however "Musk has not received anything" as yet. He and Heard split in February 2018 following an on-off relationship.Heard also told that the pair now enjoy a "beautiful friendship" based on "intellectual curiosity, ideas and conversation, a shared love for science."

Recent surveillance footage from the garage of their building has Amber Heard and Elon Musk next to each other in an Elevator, per News 18. In addition to this, a lawsuit file statement makes the following claims: 

Only one month after Mr. Depp and Ms. Heard were married - while Mr Depp was out of the country, filming in March 2015- Eastern Columbia Building personnel testified that Ms. Heard received Musk 'late night' at Mr Depp's penthouse. Specially Ms. Heard asked staff at the Eastern Columbia Building to give her friend Elon access to the building's parking garage and the penthouse elevator 'late at night' and they testified that they did so. Building staff would then see Mrs. Heard's friend Elon leaving the building the next morning. 

Heard asked a judge to dismiss the $50 million law suit on Friday. Heard filed a motion in the circuit court of Fairfax asking for the case to be struck out. She offered new details about instances in which Depp `` shaped her, shoved her, pulled her hair and choked her," AP said, providing photos as evidence. 

Since their divorce Mr Depp has continued to publically harass Ms Heard and attempted to gaslight the world by denying his abuse. It is long past time for Mr Depp's despicable conduct to end. Heard's attorney told AP. 
Depp's lawyer Waldman denied the claims and said it was Heard who abused his client. In an email to AP, he added " The only way for Amber Heard to sustain her hoax is with more lies." 

So that's all for today's video. What's your opinion on Johnny Depp's new allegation against Elon Musk?Sound off know your thoughts in the comments section below.If you have not signed in to my channel yet please do this.See you within the next video.
______________________________________________

snippet.description:
Elon Musk Challenges Johnny Depp To A ‚ÄòCage Fight‚Äô Amid Amber Heard Rumors

In case you haven‚Äôt been keeping up with the ongoing legal drama between actors Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, one of the celebrities who‚Äôs been dragged into the proceedings between the ex-couple is SpaceX founder and CEO Elon Musk, who dated Heard following her separation from Depp. Just last month, it was alleged that Musk had not only an affair with the Aquaman actress while she was still married to the Pirates of the Caribbean actor, but that Musk also had a threesome with Heard and Suicide Squad actress Cara Delevingne inside Depp‚Äôs own LA penthouse.

snippet.description: Als Zeuge geladen: Johnny Depp hofft im Rosenkrieg mit Amber Heard auf Elon Musk   Vorladung f√ºr den Tesla-Chef   ¬†Hollywood-Star Johnny Depp (57) will weiter um seine Reputation und gegen seine Ex-Frau Amber Heard (34) k√§mpfen. Nach einem erfolglosen Prozess gegen die britische Boulevardzeitung "The Sun", verklagt er Heard in Virginia wegen Verleumdung und fordert 50 Millionen US-Dollar von seiner Ex-Frau wegen eines von ihr verfassten Artikels f√ºr die "Washington Post". Hilfe verspricht sich Depp in dem Fall von Tesla-Chef Elon Musk (49). Wie "Deadline" berichtet, hat der Unternehmer von Depps Anw√§lten eine Vorladung erhalten.  ¬†Die Anw√§lte m√∂chten, dass Musk Aussagen "zu jeglicher Kommunikation zwischen Ihnen und Frau Heard in Bezug auf Herrn Depp" t√§tige. Zudem haben sie Fragen zum "Sun"-Prozess und den "Vorw√ºrfen wegen k√∂rperlichen Missbrauchs oder h√§uslicher Gewalt, die entweder von Herrn Depp oder von Frau Heard begangen wurden". Doch was hat Elon Musk mit der Angelegenheit √ºberhaupt zu tun?¬†Der Unternehmer war nach Heards Scheidung von Johnny Depp mit der Schauspielerin liiert. Dass die beiden bereits w√§hrend der Ehe eine Aff√§re und eine Dreiecksbeziehung mit Cara Delevingne (28) gehabt haben sollen, bestritt Musk im Juni 2020 gegen√ºber "Page Six", dem Klatschportal der "New York Post": "Cara und ich sind Freunde, aber wir waren nie intim. [...] Au√üerdem m√∂chte ich noch einmal betonen, dass Amber und ich erst ungef√§hr einen Monat nach ihrer Scheidung angefangen haben, auszugehen. Ich glaube nicht, dass ich w√§hrend ihrer Ehe jemals in ihrer N√§he war!"   Auch der Kampf gegen "The Sun" ist noch nicht vorbei  ¬†Ein Londoner Gericht hatte Anfang November 2020 eine Klage Depps gegen die britische Boulevardzeitung "The Sun" abgewiesen, die ihn als "Frauenschl√§ger" bezeichnet hatte. Depp und sein Anwaltsteam wollen gegen das Urteil Berufung einlegen, eine Anh√∂rung soll daf√ºr im kommenden M√§rz stattfinden. Ein Richter am Berufungsgericht verf√ºgte "Deadline" zufolge, dass Johnny Depp und sein Team eine m√ºndliche Anh√∂rung erhalten, die zwischen dem 15. und 31. M√§rz stattfinden und zwei Stunden dauern werde.¬†Der Prozess gegen die "Sun" war zu einem weiteren Rosenkrieg zwischen Depp und Heard ausgeartet, die von 2015 bis 2017 verheiratet waren. Beide erhoben schwerwiegende Vorw√ºrfe gegeneinander. Nach einem 16-t√§gigen Prozess in London kam der Richter zu dem Urteil, dass die Wortwahl "im Wesentlichen wahr" gewesen sei. Depps Anw√§lte argumentierten anschlie√üend vor dem Berufungsgericht, der Richter habe die vorgelegten Beweise von Depps Ex-Frau zu unkritisch akzeptiert, dar√ºber hinaus habe er relevante Beweise ignoriert oder gar nicht erst zugelassen.

snippet.title: Elon Musk Offered Amber Heard 24*7 Security [ Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Trial ]
snippet.description:
Elon Musk Offered Amber Heard 24*7 Security [ Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Trial ]

Elon Musk offered Amber Heard "every minute of every day security" after she revealed to him she needed a controlling request against Johnny Depp, the High Court has heard. 

She denied Elon Musk visited her while her then-spouse Johnny Depp was away. 

Johnny Depp, is suing the distributor of the Sun over an article that marked him a "tank top" - yet the paper demands it was precise. 

The US entertainer, , was giving proof in London for a second day on the eleventh day of her ex's slander activity. 

She excused recommendations Elon Musk visited her in 2015 while Johnny Depp was away, saying she was not in contact with the Tesla author until the next year. 

On Tuesday, Depp's attorney, Eleanor Laws QC, addressed Ms Heard on her announcement, in which the legal advisor said the on-screen character had demonstrated that Johnny Depp was "strangely desirous" and that she wasn't having any "unlawful connections". 

The preliminary adjudicator, Justice Nicol, interceded to state "unlawful... conveys an undertone". 

Golden Heard answered: "Not that that issues a lot, however no." 

Ms Laws concurred: "No, it doesn't. 

The legal advisor at that point read out instant messages between Amber Heard and elon Musk from 22 May 2016, in which Ms Heard told elon Musk that she would acquire a controlling request against her at that point spouse. 

The messages came a day after a supposed occurrence at the Eastern Columbia Building in Los Angeles, where Johnny Depp and golden Heard lived, in which the entertainer claims Depp tossed her cell phone at her, smacking her in the face - which the on-screen character denies. 

Addressing amber Heard, Mis Laws said elon Musk offered to "orchestrate day in and day out security for you", including that he stated: "The offer would stand, regardless of whether you never needed to see me again... anyway, upset for being a simpleton. The radio quiet damages a great deal. It just issues since I truly like you." 

The lawyer at that point alluded to prove given by Alejandro Romero, an attendant at the Eastern Columbia Building, who said he saw Musk visiting Heard "when Johnny Depp was in Australia". 

Heard said Mr Romero was "off-base", demanding that she wasn't in correspondence with elon Musk until 2016. 

In his composed observer articulation, Romero stated: "From March 2015 onwards, Ms Heard was visited normally late around evening time, at around 11pm to 12 PM, by Elon Musk." 

The attendant asserted Heard gave Musk his own coxcomb to get to the structure.

snippet.title: Johnny Depp hofft im Rosenkrieg mit Amber Heard auf Elon Musk
snippet.description: Johnny Depp hofft im Rosenkrieg mit Amber Heard auf Elon Musk   Vorladung f√ºr Tesla-Chef  ¬†Hollywood-Star Johnny Depp (57, "Das geheime Fenster") will weiter um seine Reputation und gegen seine Ex-Frau Amber Heard (34) k√§mpfen. Nach einem erfolglosen Prozess gegen die britische Boulevardzeitung "The Sun", verklagt er Heard in Virginia wegen Verleumdung und fordert 50 Millionen US-Dollar von seiner Ex-Frau wegen eines von ihr verfassten Artikels f√ºr die "Washington Post". Hilfe verspricht sich Depp in dem Fall von Tesla-Chef Elon Musk (49). Wie "Deadline" berichtet, hat der Unternehmer von Depps Anw√§lten eine Vorladung erhalten.  ¬†Die Anw√§lte m√∂chten, dass Musk Aussagen "zu jeglicher Kommunikation zwischen Ihnen und Frau Heard in Bezug auf Herrn Depp" t√§tige. Zudem haben sie Fragen zum "Sun"-Prozess und den "Vorw√ºrfen wegen k√∂rperlichen Missbrauchs oder h√§uslicher Gewalt, die entweder von Herrn Depp oder von Frau Heard begangen wurden". Doch was hat Elon Musk mit der Angelegenheit √ºberhaupt zu tun?   ¬†Der Unternehmer war nach Heards Scheidung von Johnny Depp mit der Schauspielerin liiert. Dass die beiden bereits w√§hrend der Ehe eine Aff√§re und eine Dreiecksbeziehung mit Cara Delevingne (28) gehabt haben sollen, bestritt Musk im Juni 2020 gegen√ºber "Page Six", dem Klatschportal der "New York Post": "Cara und ich sind Freunde, aber wir waren nie intim. [...] Au√üerdem m√∂chte ich noch einmal betonen, dass Amber und ich erst ungef√§hr einen Monat nach ihrer Scheidung angefangen haben, auszugehen. Ich glaube nicht, dass ich w√§hrend ihrer Ehe jemals in ihrer N√§he war!"   ¬†Auch der Kampf gegen "The Sun" ist noch nicht vorbei   ¬†Ein Londoner Gericht hatte Anfang November 2020 eine Klage Depps gegen die britische Boulevardzeitung "The Sun" abgewiesen, die ihn als "Frauenschl√§ger" bezeichnet hatte. Depp und sein Anwaltsteam wollen gegen das Urteil Berufung einlegen, eine Anh√∂rung soll daf√ºr im kommenden M√§rz stattfinden.  Ein Richter am Berufungsgericht verf√ºgte "Deadline" zufolge, dass Johnny Depp und sein Team eine m√ºndliche Anh√∂rung erhalten, die zwischen dem 15. und 31. M√§rz stattfinden und zwei Stunden dauern werde.   ¬†Der Prozess gegen die "Sun" war zu einem weiteren Rosenkrieg zwischen Depp und Heard ausgeartet, die von 2015 bis 2017 verheiratet waren. Beide erhoben schwerwiegende Vorw√ºrfe gegeneinander. Nach einem 16-t√§gigen Prozess in London kam der Richter zu dem Urteil, dass die Wortwahl "im Wesentlichen wahr" gewesen sei. Depps Anw√§lte argumentierten anschlie√üend vor dem Berufungsgericht, der Richter habe die vorgelegten Beweise von Depps Ex-Frau zu unkritisch akzeptiert, dar√ºber hinaus habe er relevante Beweise ignoriert oder gar nicht erst zugelassen.

snippet.title: Why and how the industry must change | Anna Goldhhofer | TEDxM√ºnchen
snippet.description: ‚ÄúInstead of continuing with a linear economy, let‚Äôs work towards a circular economy that enables us to use our planets resources responsibly. Let‚Äôs think in cycles.‚Äù Anna Goldhofer works from within the industry to create the change we need to tackle climate change. Anna is a sustainability expert and activist that wants industries to act circular and more responsibly. In her talk she proposes a change of mindset and gives insights how to adapt circularity within industries and explains 4 ways how to combine action with a circular economy. ‚ÄúLet‚Äôs treat this crisis like the existential emergency it is. Time is running against us.‚Äù She speaks as a sustainability expert and activist. She studied industrial engineering, what creates the basis for her broad understanding of materials, lifecycles, resource management and recycling possibilities. She understands herself as a young global citizen, aligning her daily doings with the UNs Sustainable Development Goals. Anna is highly committed to take action, to learn, to empower and to develop solutions which positively impact the future of our planet and its people. Her utmost believe is that regarding the state our planet is in, it is important to question whether what we do in our everyday life has a positive impact on the world. This talk was given at a TEDx event using the TED conference format but independently organized by a local community. Learn more at https://www.ted.com/tedx

Take a look into the family life of Elon Musk  - Tesla & SpaceX CEO - , the world‚Äôs richest man, including his two ex wives and his six kids. You will wonder what type of lifestyle do Elon‚Äôs privileged kids live, and you might be suprised by the type of father that Elon Musk is. 

#ElonMusk, #RichKids, #AdAstra

Wheter you want to learn about our Rich Journey to the Billionaire Lifestyle of famous celebrities, or about the Richest Tech Entrepreneur like Elon Musk Tesla & SpaceX CEO or TOP 10  Athletes and other mind blowing people on the Forbes list , how they spends their millions , what supercar or expensive sports car they drive, House Tour in the most expensive Real Estates in the world, money topics like tsla & bitcoin, and even some of the most mind-blowing tech news and top 10 engineering discoveries - we've got you covered.

BILLIONAIRE Elon Musk may have his hands full running various companies such as Tesla and SpaceX, but he also has six children to look after. If Elon  has a trip for Tesla to China, for example, he bring the kids with him and they‚Äôll go see the Great Wall or they took the bullet train from Beijing to Xian and saw the Terracotta Warriors. 
Elon Musk Tesla & SpaceX CEO first child, Nevada Alexander Musk, was born in 2002, two years after he married Canadian author Justine Wilson Elon Musk‚Äôs Ex  Wife in 2000. Sadly, he died at just 10 weeks old of sudden infant death syndrome. In 2004, Musk and then-wife Justine  welcomed twins Griffin and Xavier.The twins, who are now 17, were conceived through In vitro fertilisation. The former couple's triplets Kai, Saxon and Damian Musk were born in 2006  and they too were conceived through In vitro fertilisation . On May 5, 2020, Elon Musk and his partner Grimes singer song writer  announced the arrival of their little boy.The pair initially named their newborn child  X √Ü A-12.

Due to his innovative and eccentric nature, Musk did not want to take his children to a traditional elite school. "I hated going to school when I was little, it was torture," confessed Musk, who was bullied as a child in South Africa. So in 2014 he decided to found his own school - named Ad-Astra -with his own methodology , supported by a former teacher at the Mirman School for Gifted Children , located in Beverly Hills, Los Angeles, which his children used to attend. 
Elon Musk‚Äôs kids are also fortunate enough to have a wealthy father that can afford to take them anywhere around the world. ‚Ä¶. And beyond ‚Ä¶ As Elon Musk just bought a ticket to space from fellow space billionaire Richard Branson‚Äôs Virgin Galactic. Elon‚Äôs sons growing up with a whole set of experiences that quiet luxurious and unusual for most kids their age.

Here's an inside look at the daily life and routine of one of the world's most influential people, Elon Musk. The founder of PayPal, Tesla Motors, SpaceX, and more is one of the busiest people on earth.

"Nobody ever changed the world on 40 hours a week." These are the words of multi-billionaire entrepreneur Elon Musk, who not only runs two of the most innovative companies of current times, Tesla and SpaceX, but also juggles travel, interviews, and a family of 5 teenage sons on a daily basis.

It's no secret that Elon Musk's fruitful ventures have been built off the back of hard work, dedication, and smart decision making ‚Äì but what about the details? Wouldn't it be great to see how the most influential man in the world organizes his time and manages to cram everything into a seemingly impossible schedule?

snippet.title: Did Amber Heard, Elon Musk just confirm their relationship? - Hollywood News
snippet.description:
New Delhi, Apr 25 (ANI): It seems Amber Heard and Elon Musk are more than just a fling. Amber Heard made the couple`s romance official by sharing a photo on Instagram of herself resting her arm against Musk. The 31-year-old-actress captioned the snap, "Cheeky." The photo also shows a kiss-mark on Musk's right cheek, which is clearly visible. Earlier, the 'Danish Girl' star and Tesla founder were spotted together for the first time in public while in Australia, where the actress is currently filming her upcoming movie 'Aquaman,' according to People Magazine. The couple spent Sunday at the Gold Coast's Currumbin Wildlife Sanctuary, where they walked arm-in-arm through the reserve. Amber Heard filed for divorce from Johnny Depp in last May and their divorce was finalised in January 2017, whereas Elon Musk filed for divorce from wife Talulah Riley in January 2015 and has five sons from previous marriage.

snippet.title: Grimes Claps Back At Elon Musk For Correcting Explanation Of Son's Name
snippet.description:
Here's some important advice: If you're a dad, never correct your partner's misspellings just after she's given birth. Elon Musk found that out when he tried to correct his beau after she misspelled their newborn baby's name on Twitter.

The couple, who started dating in May 2018, welcomed a son together on May 4, 2020. Given the fact that they named him "X √Ü A-12 Musk," some confusion regarding the announcement was bound to happen.

Yes, X √Ü A-12 Musk. That‚Äôs the name of their son, and Grimes explained that the "A-12" portion is inspired by the couple's favorite aircraft, the SR-17. That, as it turns out, wasn't quite right -- and Elon Musk wasted no time in pointing Grimes' mistake out on Twitter.

Come find out more about why and how Grimes clapped back the origin of their child‚Äôs name.

AMBER HEARD PANICS as Baby Daddy ELON MUSK IS SUED For Billions | The Gossipy

There are plenty of rumors that Elon Musk and Amber Heard are still romantically involved. Elon Musk is being sued for a large amount of money. 

Elon Musk just keeps getting dragged back into the Johnny Depp Amber Heard celeb drama. Elon Musk, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are back on the frontlines of celebrity news. Amber Heard just had a baby girl and rumors are swirling on who the baby's father is. 

Many are saying it is Johnny Depp. Some are saying is Elon Musk himself. Elon Musk and Amber Heard are past lovers and rumors are swirling that Elon Musk paid Amber Heard's 7 million donation to the ACLU back in 2016. So these two have a history together.

But no public statements have been made in this regard by either Elon Musk, Johnny Depp or Amber Heard. So no one knows for sure yet. In this video, we breakdown the story in detail. This celebrity drama goes down while the Johnny Depp Amber Heard civil court case rages on.

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. snippet.title: Johnny Depp reveals ex wife Amber Heard cheated on him with Elon Musk report
snippet.description:
Hollywood actor Johnny Depp has reportedly claimed that his ex-wife Amber Heard cheated on him with Elon Musk during their marriage. 

As per reports, the actor revealed that Heard had invited Musk to their penthouse when Depp was away to shoot for his film. The staff at Johnny Depp's penthouse has reportedly confirmed that Musk arrived late at night and left the next morning.

The lawsuit filed by Depp further mentions that the staff at Depp's penthouse had reportedly given access to the garage and elevator. News reports further add that Amber Heard had shown violent behaviour toward Johnny Depp in Australia when the latter wanted a post-nuptial agreement with respect to their assets.  

'The Pirates of the Caribbean' actor has received the court's permission to go ahead with his defamation case against former wife Amber Heard. 

As per the media reports, the actress, in an article,  had revealed details of her experience of domestic violence without particularly naming Johhny Depp. 'The Aquaman' actress stated that she faced the worst force of their culture.

The court has allowed Johnny Depp to go forward with his legal case against former wife under the assumption that she aimed her allegations of domestic violence on him.

As per reports, the actor revealed that Heard had invited Musk to their penthouse when Depp was away to shoot for his film. The staff at Johnny Depp's penthouse has reportedly confirmed that Musk arrived late at night and left the next morning.

The lawsuit filed by Depp further mentions that the staff at Depp's penthouse had reportedly given access to the garage and elevator. News reports further add that Amber Heard had shown violent behaviour toward Johnny Depp in Australia when the latter wanted a post-nuptial agreement with respect to their assets.  

'The Pirates of the Caribbean' actor has received the court's permission to go ahead with his defamation case against former wife Amber Heard. 

As per the media reports, the actress, in an article,  had revealed details of her experience of domestic violence without particularly naming Johhny Depp. 'The Aquaman' actress stated that she faced the worst force of their culture.

The court has allowed Johnny Depp to go forward with his legal case against former wife under the assumption that she aimed her allegations of domestic violence on him.

 The Mera of DC Extended Universe is reportedly embroiled in a legal battle with the Tesla mogul over the rights to embryos they created during their relationship.  Jul 31, 2020  ¬†AceShowbiz - Amber Heard was reportedly locked in a legal battle with ex-lover Elon Musk over the "Aquaman" actress' frozen embryos.  ¬† In documents obtained by Britain's Daily Mirror newspaper, Jennifer Howell - a pal of Heard's sister Whitney Henriquez and mum Paige - revealed the latter told her that billionaire Musk was suing the actress. ¬† ¬†   ¬† "Paige told me.... she was in a legal battle with him over the rights to embryos they had created together," she shared. "He wanted to destroy them, and Amber tried to keep them to have a baby."  ¬† Comparing Musk to Heard's ex-husband Johnny Depp, Howell said, "Paige told me that Johnny was either an angel or a saint compared to Elon."  ¬† Howell made the claims in a U.S. libel trial Depp has brought against Heard, and her statement will be used as evidence in the ...

snippet.title: Amber Heard parties with boyfriend Elon Musk after they were pictured kissing on a dinner date
snippet.description: Amber Heard parties with boyfriend Elon Musk after they were pictured kissing on a dinner date.AMBER Heard partied until the early hours with boyfriend Elon Musk over the weekend - fuelling claims the pair are very much back together following their August split.The pair were pictured laughing with friends inside West Hollywood's The Abbey on Saturday, with TMZ claiming that the pair headed into the venue at around 1am.Images show the Justice League actress, 31, wrapping her arms around a pal while the Tesla founder, 46, stood close behind her. According to the outlet, Amber and the business magnate went wild when the venue started playing Cardi B's Bodak Yellow.

snippet.title: 15 Crazy Rules Elon Musk Forces His Girlfriends To Follow
snippet.description:
Take A Look At The Rules He Wants His Or Wives Or Girlfriends To Follow
Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Subscribe-to-Talko
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

If the difference between weird and eccentric is money, Elon Musk moved from weird to eccentric long ago. The controversy-tweeting billionaire has a longer list of must-haves rivals than even Leonardo DiCaprio, who also prefers young blondes. Some of the tech mogul‚Äôs demands are quite reasonable; like getting along with his kids, or not starting drama with his exs, but others are quite strange - must have blonde hair seems like a shallow enough preference, but what about not being allowed to cancel plans? Or that Musk refuses to sleep alone, and requires a younger partner to become a trophy girlfriend? The Tesla CEO has always wanted a ‚Äòsoulmate‚Äù and is very serious when it comes to dating. Not interested in flings, Musk is seeking someone who can work around his busy schedule, and love his children, He reportedly ‚Äúdoesn't like being lonely‚Äù, refuses to sleep alone, and is persistent when it comes to chasing romance. Musk is reportedly a very caring father, and always ensures his partners are cared for, even post-breakup. After having five children with his first wife, and marrying the same woman twice, Musk has dated an impressive list of stars ‚Äì From Cameron Diaz to Amber Heard, and current partner Grimes, with whom Musk shares a son. It is no secret that the billionaire inventor prefers younger partners, and while he will discuss his profound loneliness, there are a few things Musk will not discuss, even with long-term partners. To rank as potential girlfriend material, Musk only requires a few things, like having blonde hair, an artsy career, and to prioritize his career.

snippet.title: Amber Heard Seen Cuddling With Elon Musk In Johnny Depp's Elevator
snippet.description:
Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's relationship was filled with scandals and reports of he said, she said. Just a few years ago, Depp was painted as an abuser although thanks to recently released footage, it was revealed that Heard was the one allegedly doing the abuse. Now, Depp is suing Heard for defamation with requested damages of $50 million. Thanks to recent footage obtained by the Daily Mail, it looks like Elon Musk will find himself thrust into the thick of the drama.

It's been well-documented that Heard allegedly began an affair with Musk just a month into her marriage with Depp back in 2015. Heard and Musk have been adamant that it started after Depp and the actress split up. However, in the footage found here, Heard can be seen snuggling up to Musk in an elevator at the building that Depp owned penthouses at. It's pretty damning evidence that doesn't help Heard's case.
Due to Heard's accusations against Depp, he has lost his role as Jack Sparrow in the Pirates of the Caribbean and has been the subject of scrutiny from the media. With new evidence in mind, it looks like Depp's defamation lawsuit is starting to pick up steam.

Stay tuned for updates on this story as we will be sure to bring them to you.

snippet.title: Elon Musk Talks Heartbreak
snippet.description:
In a recent, in-depth Rolling Stone interview, Elon Musk got candid about his personal life. Expressing his heartbreak over their parting, he spoke of his recent breakup with ex-girlfriend Amber Heard. It's an usual move for Musk. In 2010 he said that he would "rather stick a fork in my hand than write about my personal life."
The CEO of Tesla and SpaceX went on to discuss how difficult it is for him to meet people. He says he is looking for a long-term relationship ‚Äî and a soul mate. Musk even asked interviewer Neil Strauss if there was anyone Strauss thought he should date. He told Rolling Stone, "If I'm not in love, if I'm not with a long-term companion, I cannot be happy. I will never be happy without having someone."

snippet.title: Amber Heard and Elon Musk Vacationing in Chile Together, One Week After Kissing Photos
snippet.description:
Amber Heard and Elon Musk Vacationing in Chile Together, One Week After Kissing Photos
 A  week  after  dismissing  reports  that  they're  not  a couple,  Amber Heard  and  Elon Musk  were  spotted  dining  in  Chile  together  on  Friday  night.
A  week  ago  the  former  couple  sparked  rumors  that  they  were  back  together  when  they  were  spotted  kissing  after  having  lunch  together  in  Los Angeles,  but  the  reconciliation  rumblings  were  quickly  shut down.
 Two  days  after  break-up  reports  surfaced,  Musk  eventually  addressed  split  rumors  on  social media  on  Aug.  8,  writing,  "Btw,  just  to  clear  up  some  of  the press  storm  this  weekend,  although  Amber  and  I did  break up,  we  are  still  friends,  remain  close  and  love  one  another."
Hours  later,  Heard  posted  her  own  Instagram  confirming  the  split  and  elaborating  on  the  breakup:  "Being  in  the public  eye  means  having  to  explain  yourself  to  so  many people,  so much  of  the  time.  In  this  case,  I'd  like  to  remain  more  quiet.  Although  we  have  broken up,  Elon  and  I  care  deeply  for  one  another  and  remain  close.  Thank you  for  the  continued  support,  respect,  and  privacy  during  these  difficult,  very  human  times."
 While  reports  linked  the  two  as  early  as  summer  of  2016  following  sightings  of  them  together  out  in  South Beach  and  partying  in  London,  the  couple  didn't  go  public  with  their  romance  until  April  2017.
In  the  weeks  that  followed,  they  were  spotted  strolling  during  a  day  date  at  a  wildlife  sanctuary  in  Australia,  having fun  with  Musk's  sons  at  the  Sydney Opera House  and  walking  arm  in  arm  after  a  fancy  night  out.

snippet.title: COULD AMBER HEARD SOON BE AMBER MUSK?
snippet.description:
Have you heard what's happening with Amber and Elon? Amber Heard is reportedly getting very serious with billionaire boo Elon Musk!


Amber Heard definitely got an upgrade! But Tesla billionaire Elon Musk has to be pretty happy. Sources say the guy has been waiting for Amber since 2013, after they met on the set of Machete Kills.


Musk and Heard are both recently divorced. Elon Musk was married to Talulah Riley. They were married in 2010, got divorced in 2012 and remarried in 2013. The two called it quits again in March of this year. Prior to Talulah Riley, Musk was married to Justine Wilson; they shared six children. One unfortunately passed. Amber Heard, on the other-hand, recently had a very messy divorce with Johnny Depp involving abuse allegations.

 
Does anyone smell that musk? Must be love in the air!

snippet.title: Elon Musk Dating Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Is Amber Heard, who is currently going through a nasty divorce with Johnny Depp, being comforted by Elon Musk?

Elon Musk's Rep Denies He's Dating Amber Heard

Amber Heard & Elon Musk Date Night: Moving On From Johnny Depp? 

Is Amber Heard Dating Elon Musk Now That She Has Left Johnny Depp?

Elon Musk & Amber Heard Dating After Johnny Depp Split? They're Hanging Out A Lot

Rumors swirl that Amber Heard is dating Elon Musk 


Johnny Depp's estranged wife Amber Heard and SpaceX billionaire Elon Musk 'are not dating .

According to a source, the beautiful actress spent the weekend at the Delano South Beach with the single-again Tesla billionaire.

While those close to both Musk and Heard insist they are just friends, spies tell Page Six that, although they had separate rooms, Musk was seen entering a specific room and the actress exiting the same room at different times over four days.

One witness said, ‚ÄúThey were seen arriving to, and leaving, the same room many times, but always separately. He was seen going in at night and doing a ‚Äòwalk of shame‚Äô in the morning.‚Äù

Musk was in Florida for the launch of a SpaceX rocket from Cape Canaveral, while Heard was there for work, we‚Äôre told.

But sources close to both Heard and Musk insist they are friends and he allowed her to use his room while he was working on his rocket launch.

‚ÄúI believe your sources are mistaken,‚Äù Musk‚Äôs rep told us. ‚ÄúElon was in Cape Canaveral, Florida, for a SpaceX rocket launch this weekend.‚Äù Cape Canaveral is three hours‚Äô drive from Miami, and Musk posted tweets from the Falcon launch on July 17 and 18. Of his ‚Äúwalk of shame‚Äù the rep echoed, ‚ÄúDon‚Äôt think that last bit is true, unfortunately.‚Äù


Elon Reeve Musk (/ÀàiÀêl…ín Ààm åsk/; born June 28, 1971) is a South African-born Canadian-American business magnate, investor[10][11] engineer[12] and inventor.[13][14][15][16]

He is the founder, CEO and CTO of SpaceX; co-founder, CEO and product architect of Tesla Motors; co-founder and chairman of SolarCity, co-chairman of OpenAI; co-founder of Zip2; and founder of X.com which merged with PayPal of Confinity.[17][18][19] As of June 2016, he has an estimated net worth of US$12.7 billion, making him the 83rd wealthiest person in the world.[20]

Musk has stated that the goals of SolarCity, Tesla Motors, and SpaceX revolve around his vision to change the world and humanity.[21] His goals include reducing global warming through sustainable energy production and consumption, and reducing the "risk of human extinction" by "making life multiplanetary"[22][23] by setting up a human colony on Mars. Musk was in Florida for the launch of a SpaceX rocket from Cape Canaveral, while Heard was there for work, we‚Äôre told.

But sources close to both Heard and Musk insist they are friends and he allowed her to use his room while he was working on his rocket launch.

‚ÄúI believe your sources are mistaken,‚Äù Musk‚Äôs rep told us. ‚ÄúElon was in Cape Canaveral, Florida, for a SpaceX rocket launch this weekend.‚Äù Cape Canaveral is three hours‚Äô drive from Miami, and Musk posted tweets from the Falcon launch on July 17 and 18. Of his ‚Äúwalk of shame‚Äù the rep echoed, ‚ÄúDon‚Äôt think that last bit is true, unfortunately.‚Äù


Elon Reeve Musk (/ÀàiÀêl…ín Ààm åsk/; born June 28, 1971) is a South African-born Canadian-American business magnate, investor[10][11] engineer[12] and inventor.[13][14][15][16]

He is the founder, CEO and CTO of SpaceX; co-founder, CEO and product architect of Tesla Motors; co-founder and chairman of SolarCity, co-chairman of OpenAI; co-founder of Zip2; and founder of X.com which merged with PayPal of Confinity.[17][18][19] As of June 2016, he has an estimated net worth of US$12.7 billion, making him the 83rd wealthiest person in the world.[20]

Musk has stated that the goals of SolarCity, Tesla Motors, and SpaceX revolve around his vision to change the world and humanity.[21] His goals include reducing global warming through sustainable energy production and consumption, and reducing the "risk of human extinction" by "making life multiplanetary"[22][23] by setting up a human colony on Mars. snippet.title: Amber Heard is Planning to Wed Billionaire Boyfriend Elon Musk and Hopes to Start a Family Together
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is Planning to Wed Billionaire Boyfriend Elon Musk and Hopes to Start a Family Together.

Her bitter divorce with ex-husband Johnny Depp finally went through in January this year. But Amber Heard has seemingly not been put off marriage and is said to be 'making plans' to wed billionaire boyfriend Elon Musk. The 30-year-old actress is looking to 'settle down and have a family' with the Tesla boss, her father has revealed.

Amber's father David told Grazia magazine, 'Amber and Elon are both very serious about each other. She would love to get married. 

'One of the things they want to do is settle down and have a family. They are making plans for that.' Amber was first linked to Musk last summer, after the pair were spotted together on several occasions both in London and Miami.

The Rum Diary actress is said to be 'smitten' with Musk following her divorce with Johnny. A source told the Mirror in January, 'Amber is over the moon about her divorce but she is even happier about being able to go public with Elon.'She was telling friends over Christmas how smitten she is with Elon. 'They are already planning a lot of adventures together and she's relieved she can move on with her life. It's an exciting new chapter for both of them.'

Musk, who is reportedly worth an eye-watering ¬£9.2billion - reportedly 'became infatuated' with Amber after the two appeared in the 2013 film Machete Kills, according to The Hollywood Reporter.

snippet.title: Elon Musk Girlfriends List: Dating History
snippet.description:
A worldwide known billionaire Elon Musk is always surrounded by Hollywood beauties. Perhaps, that‚Äôs why the list of his ex-wives and girlfriends is not that short. So, let‚Äôs have a look at Tesla's founder relationships, marriages, divorces and kids. 

Justine Wilson
2000-2008

She is now a well-known Canadian author, who had been married to Musk for 8 years. The couple began dating when both of them were studying at the Ontario‚Äôs Queen University. Soon after their wedding, they welcomed a firstborn, a son who they named Nevada. Unfortunately, at the age of just 10 weeks he passed away from a sudden infant syndrome. Later, Justine and Elon became parents to twins in 2004 and triplets in 2006. And even though they were raising five kids together, they filed for a divorce after eight years of married life. They remained close and co-parent the kids.

Talulah Riley
2008-2016

After the spit from the first spouse, the founder of SpaceX got romantically involved with a British actress. After two years of being together, they tied the knot officially and had been a happy married couple until they called it quits in 2012. Nonetheless, this breakup didn‚Äôt last long and they got hitched again in 2013. In 2014 Musk filed for a second divorce but it was later withdrawn. In 2016, the media started saying that their divorce proceedings were underway once again. And this time it was true, with Riley herself filing for a divorce from her husband. That same year everything was successfully finalized. They split on good terms and frequently see each other.

Cameron Diaz
March-May 2013

According to some sources, after the first divorce from Riley, Elon had a short-term affair with a famous Hollywood movie star. Their romance started after Diaz purchased a Tesla. Although, it ended as quickly as it began. 

Amber Heard
2016-2018

The relationship between these two love birds had been on and off since 2016 till 2018. When Heard divorced Johnny Depp, she found her happiness in Musk. They were often spotted together at various events between 2016 and 2017. In early 2018 they tried to get the feelings back but decided that it would be better to walk separate ways. Nowadays, even though they are not together anymore, they still care for each other.

Grimes
2018-present time

For many people, this couple is very bizarre and most probably won‚Äôt last long. Musk and an indie musician met over Twitter when they both joked about artificial intelligence online. Soon after that, they came together arm-in-arm at the 2018 Met Gala. They were even spotted together at Kim Kardashian‚Äôs Christmas party with Kim taking a picture with them and uploading it on social media. At the beginning of 2020 Grimes shared a picture on Instagram and wrote about her pregnancy. In the revealed photo one can clearly see a baby bump, meaning that Elon is going to be a father for the sixth time.
Do you want to see more?

snippet.title: Elon Musk REVEALED The SHOCKING TRUTH About Bill Gates!
snippet.description:
Elon Musk, SpaceX and Tesla

Last year during the pandemic Elon Musk doubled down on Covid-19 skepticism and said that he won't take future vaccines. Musk even called the pandemic quarantine facist.
In an interview on CNBC's "Squawk Box," Gates criticized Musk's controversial comments on the virus and implied that Musk shouldn't be speaking about the pandemic at all. He said,
‚ÄúElon‚Äôs positioning is to maintain a high level of outrageous comments,‚Äù Gates said. ‚ÄúHe‚Äôs not much involved in vaccines. He makes a great electric car. And his rockets work well. So he‚Äôs allowed to say these things. I hope that he doesn‚Äôt confuse areas he‚Äôs not involved in too much.‚Äù
Musk, the South African born billionaire was enraged by Gates' remarks and mocked him on Twitter. He jokingly posted multiple tweets about Gates, including ‚ÄúBilly G is not my lover‚Äù and ‚Äúthe rumour that Bill Gates & I are lovers is completely untrue.‚Äù
Musk defended himself against Gates‚Äô comments, saying he‚Äôd spent time with Harvard University epidemiologists ‚Äúdoing antibody studies‚Äù and noting Tesla‚Äôs work with CureVac.
Later in an interview with  journalist Kara Swisher Musk said bluntly that "Gates said something about me not knowing what I was doing. It's like, hey, knucklehead, we actually make the vaccine machines for CureVac, that company you're invested in."
Elon Musk, however, is involved in fighting the coronavirus. The billionaire redirected Tesla resources to source and produce ventilators. He also teamed up with the German biotech firm CureVac to make a device to aid in vaccine production. Bill Gates, on the other hand, who is also a known philanthropist, is also the investor in CureVac and pledged US$100 million to fight the virus via the Bill and Melinda Gates Foundation.
Musk has frequently downplayed the severity of the virus and strongly criticised stay-at-home orders. He promoted the malaria drug hydroxychloroquine as a treatment for the virus, falsely said that children are immune to it, and questioned data regarding coronavirus deaths.

snippet.title: Johnny Depp challenged to cage fight by Elon Musk over Amber Heard affair rumour
snippet.description: Johnny Depp has been challenged to a cage fight by Elon Musk after evidence was given in court claiming Depp believed the billionaire had been having an affair with actress Amber Heard during her relationship with the Pirates of the Caribbean actor. ¬†London's High Court heard how Musk visited Heard at the Los Angeles penthouse she shared with Depp during their marriage.  ¬†Musk has denied sleeping with Heard behind Depp's back and has jokingly challenged the actor to a "cage fight" after claims were made in court that Depp had threatened to cut off Musk's manhood. ¬†He said his relationship with Heard started after she had filed for divorce. ¬† Musk, 49, told the New York Times: "I definitely was not having an affair with Amber while she was married to Johnny, this is totally false."  ¬† Asked about claims made in legal documents that he had a threesome with Heard, 34, and model Cara Delevingne, 27, in Depp‚Äôs penthouse, Musk said: "We did not have the threesome, you know.  "So I think people think these things are generally more salacious than they are."  Musk added to the publication: "Well, yeah, I hope he recovers from this situation.  "If Johnny wants a cage fight, just let me know."  ¬† Depp and Heard's turbulent relationship has been laid bare during a three week High Court showdown against The Sun.  Depp is suing the publication and its Executive Editor for libel after they branded him a 'wife beater' in a comment piece in 2018.  The piece criticised Harry Potter author JK Rowling for "standing by" Depp and keeping him in her Fantastic Beasts movie franchise.   ¬† Depp's ex-wife Amber Heard appeared in the courts as a key witness for the defence.  Johnny categorically denies claims that he was physically violent to Heard during their relationship.  Heard claims Depp was violent towards her 14 times.

snippet.title: Elon Musk TO TAKE STAND In Johnny Depp Amber Heard Court Hearing?!
snippet.description:
From a sweep-you-off-your-feet kind of romance, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard‚Äôs love story has taken a messy turn in just a few years. Five years after Amber Heard filed for divorce, the fight between the former couple is still ongoing. And even though the divorce had been finalized four years ago, the chaos that their marriage brought is far from over. Being a celebrity is a strange thing, as your personal relationships can become very public affairs. Amber Heard and Johnny Depp know this all too well, as the former couple is consistently making headlines due to their ongoing legal battle. But they made it to the headlines again, this time bringing another high profile witness‚Äôs name with them‚Ä¶ Elon Musk. Elon Musk is an entrepreneur and business magnate. He is the founder, CEO, and Chief Engineer at SpaceX; early stage investor, CEO, and Product Architect of Tesla, Inc.; founder of The Boring Company; and co-founder of Neuralink and OpenAI. A centibillionaire, Elon Musk is the richest person in the world as of September 2021. So yeah, there is no doubt there that Amber Heard would replace Johnny Depp in a split second just to get some of that. After all, wasn‚Äôt she accused of marrying Johnny Depp for his money once? So this is no news to everyone. What seems to be the news is the fact that Elon Musk might appear on the most awaited Johnny Depp and Amber Heard trial. Why, you ask? Well, there is a whole load of history we have to go through to understand, so make sure you stay until the end of this video. But before anything else, make sure to hit that subscribe button first and smash that notification bell for more updates. Now, let‚Äôs begin!

Amber Heard and Johnny Depp have been battling in court for years now, and are showing no signs of slowing down. Especially not now. There has been tons of evidence in the past years that may be helpful for the case, like the proof through phone records that Amber was really the one who hurt Johnny, the alleged affairs of Amber with actor James Franco and mega businessman Elon Musk, which somehow turned out to be true because right after she divorced Johnny, she latched onto Elon for a whole year. 

But, there has recently been another update on the excruciatingly long wait for the Johnny Depp - Amber Heard trial. Elon Musk just keeps getting dragged back into the Johnny Depp Amber Heard celeb drama. Elon Musk, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are back on the frontlines of celebrity news. Amber Heard just had a baby girl and rumors are swirling on who the baby's father is. Many are saying it is Johnny Depp. Some are saying is Elon Musk himself. Elon Musk and Amber Heard are past lovers and rumors are swirling that Elon Musk paid Amber Heard's 7 million donation to the ACLU back in 2016. So these two have a history together.

But no public statements have been made in this regard by either Elon Musk, Johnny Depp or Amber Heard. So no one knows for sure yet. In this video, we breakdown the story in detail. This celebrity drama goes down while the Johnny Depp Amber Heard civil court case rages on.

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. Her team has been working tirelessly in order to back up her side, however Johnny Depp seems to have made the attempt to strike back.

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnny

snippet.title: Amber Heard spending time with Elon Musk
snippet.description:
There may be electricity flying between Amber Heard and billionaire Elon Musk amid the actress' high profile and nasty divorce from Johnny Depp.

The 30-year-old starlet is reportedly "spending time" with the mogul behind Tesla Motors and SpaceX, TMZ reported Thursday.

Musk, who is also going through a divorce, and Heard have apparently been friends for years and have been seeing each other more in the last few months, according to the gossip site.

Two weeks ago they allegedly enjoyed a dinner date and last weekend, Heard and her sister hung out in Musk's hotel in Miami.

Reps for the stars did not immediately return the News request for comment.

Heard filed for divorce from the "Pirates of the Caribbean Star" in late May ‚Äî three days after his mom, Betty Sue Palmer, died.

Four days later, the "Danish Girl" star appeared in court bearing a visible bruise on her face and alleged a history of domestic abuse throughout their 15 month marriage.

She was granted a temporary restraining order against the actor.

Meanwhile, Musk's wife, actress Talulah Riley, filed for divorce in late March. Riley had first filed to end the marriage in 2012 but the rocky pair remarried in 2013.

A year later, it was Musk,45, who wanted out, filing for divorce on New Year's Eve 2014. The papers were dismissed six months later.

Amber and Elon have been friends for several years, according to TMZ, but since her split with Johnny, ‚Äúthey‚Äôve been spending a lot of time together.‚Äù


‚ÄúJust last weekend, Amber and her sister were hanging out in Elon‚Äôs hotel bungalow in Miami. She had a 1-on-1 dinner at his L.A. house 2 weeks ago. She recently went to Elon‚Äôs L.A. area office to spend time with him. And he‚Äôs paid several visits to her home,‚Äù a source told the news site.

At this time, no one in Amber‚Äôs circle is calling it ‚Äúdating,‚Äù but their extra time together seems super suspicious.

Interestingly, Elon is also going through a divorce. His ex filed in March after they got married for a second time. Elon is worth an estimated $12.7 billion.

As you‚Äôll recall, Amber filed for divorce and got a restraining order against the Edward Scissorhands actor earlier this year, when she accused him of physically abusing her on a number of occasions. He has denied these claims, and their divorce is still pending.
